[04:36:33.472] [INFO ]     NovaLens ships with the following out-of-the-box connectors (exact names as they appear in the UI):
    
    Relational / MPP  
    - Amazon Redshift  
    - Google BigQuery  
    - Microsoft SQL Server  
    - MySQL  
    - Oracle  
    - PostgreSQL  
    - Snowflake  
    - Teradata  
    
    Cloud file & object stores  
    - Amazon S3  
    - Azure Data Lake Storage (Gen 2)  
    - Google Cloud Storage  
    
    NoSQL & document  
    - MongoDB  
    - Cassandra / Astra DB  
    
    Streaming & message bus  
    - Apache Kafka (Confluent Cloud & on-prem)  
    - Amazon Kinesis  
    - Google Pub/Sub  
    
    Application / SaaS  
    - Salesforce  
    - ServiceNow  
    - Workday  
    - NetSuite  
    - SAP (ECC & S/4 HANA via OData & RFC)  
    - Jira (Cloud & Data Center)  
    - Coupa  
    - Zendesk  
    - HubSpot  
    - Marketo  
    - Google Analytics 4  
    - Adobe Analytics  
    
    On-prem file & legacy  
    - SFTP / FTPS  
    - HDFS  
    - IBM i (DB2 for i)  
    - AS/400 (via JD Edwards connector)  
    
    BI & semantic layers  
    - Tableau (extract & live)  
    - Power BI (Premium & Pro)  
    - Looker  
    
    All connectors support full or incremental extract, schema-on-read inference, and push-down SQL where the source allows.
